title: "Institutionalizationn"
date: 2025-06-10
categories: Philosophy
---

"The political disposition, patriotism pure and simple, is certainty based on truth—mere subjective certainty is not the outcome of truth but is only opinion—and volition which has become habitual.
As such, it is simply a product of the institutions subsisting in the state." (R, §268)
